{"tid":1230602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港今次真係大和解，大團結。","createTime":"2019-06-16T08:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:57:36.000Z","uid":35190,"like":1399,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"042d40e70390cf71095b2f1788c664f539c5171f","tid":1230602,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"搭緊巴士，今次真係做到社會各界都表左態同出一分力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括但不止於：<br />\n會計界（Big4)<br />\n銀行界（三大銀行）<br />\n教育界（教協、校長聯署）<br />\n運輸界（一眾巴士、地鐵司機大佬）<br />\n裝修界（平價賣裝備）<br />\n園藝界（平價/義送花）<br />\n殯儀界（義士哀悼）<br />\n飲食界（堅守崗位已經係）<br />\n公務員（反對既不在小數）<br />\n文藝界（導演、KoL)<br />\n學生們（中學生、大專生、熱心校友）<br />\n等等不能盡錄！！！<br />\n<br />\n大是大非前，香港人一條心！<br />\n亦證明不同界別都可以以自己既方式支持抗爭。<br />\n請補充！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c590b8399a044da0258993ed314b5d11a7259b","tid":1230602,"uid":35190,"like":647,"dislike":3,"score":644,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"宗教界（天主教、基督教、佛教等等）<br />\n社工界（社工姐姐、難民之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n泛民議員們（鄺神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"be458fd9d086e16a2edc382962be134992504daf","tid":1230602,"uid":237562,"like":150,"dislike":3,"score":147,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"嗰日坐gogovan<br />\n個司機都林病"},{"pid":"1c6dbdefae8a7d6bce6fd487f193a8ce719038e0","tid":1230602,"uid":194398,"like":245,"dislike":1,"score":244,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ad39048af3ff821381827f60f3510bbb2fb9958","tid":1230602,"uid":111751,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"好彩工程界仲係清泉"},{"pid":"24e597aeeb31dfe85b8d0e3541984d098ba93ec8","tid":1230602,"uid":186152,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"We connect <br />\n林奠港獨台獨之母"},{"pid":"952d1c647bb98d89423bdd3e4fe2f9d40d246da8","tid":1230602,"uid":229955,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d382ef7bda4ce2349c9fc6468ffeac91ea18a049","tid":1230602,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:01:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c014394b9c60a18bb5ce529f48918fd2ff3e77ae","tid":1230602,"uid":35190,"like":175,"dislike":2,"score":173,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"外國勢力助攻系列（排名不分先後）：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣<br />\n南韓<br />\n日本<br />\n德國<br />\n美國<br />\n法國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face